{"tid":269100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整合-#未來撚阿廢 既未來爆料post報告，大家可以不理","createTime":"2017-06-03T13:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T02:54:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac25eab75824b2b263dcbe8c9dd108a445b97211","tid":269100,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"呢條弱智仔，我會不斷追住佢唔放<br />\n<br />\n因為我聽開fb爆料post<br />\nfb神仙講過，共產黨培訓緊一個呢類爆料人出來，在討論區收fans，先開始懷疑佢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未來弱智仔 估中既內容，全部都係中聯辦會知道晒既野<br />\n<br />\n1. 特狗票數<br />\n(中聯辦 基本神早知道晒所有共匪投票意向，如過真是未來來，點會記唔到777，因為當時中聯辦都怕有游離票)<br />\n2.波叔財爺<br />\n3.歌女做唔到教育局<br />\n<br />\n呢3樣如果佢係中聯辦特派，知道並不難。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後其他爆料又9吹幾年後，無可能短期實現既事<br />\n什麼北泡，侵侵連任，呢d無5年都證實唔到<br />\n<br />\n而我及各巴打比佢既問題佢一概不答，有留意我追擊佢既問題都簡單合情合理，未來撚無可能不識。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑佢的疑點好合理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引申1<br />\n佢每次技窮，都會搬出對方是5毛，之後轉移視線<br />\n唔答人野，大家活係 高/連登 多年，邊班人長期掛對方是5毛係口邊，大家都明。<br />\n<br />\n引申2<br />\n仲有，佢自稱反5毛，真係有出過幾個post<br />\n不過對抗大量5毛既 郭文貴post，真係未見過佢囉<br />\n講句支那都唔敢<br />\n<br />\n引申3<br />\n巴打問親支那會唔會收皮既問題，一概不答。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會繼續update<br />\n我不介意被人說是5毛，因為唔係唔會你講2句就會係，這就是 香港人 和 支那人 的分別。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議大家睇下佢今日既 未來人報告6 睇下佢點樣技窮法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"169d44d4172d3020d9cbacbecc70f4ec64cdf452","tid":269100,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c19bf4c66017ab1dbc0bca9f153eccdc723a6a","tid":269100,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:52:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">叫人講 5毛死全家 唔講就係5毛，呢d咩野纙緝？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係支那人既纙緝<br />\n同要人道歉，要人認 既行為同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，強大的歐美，絕對唔會咁<br />\n因為我地講求心照纙緝</span>"},{"pid":"bc4cfb984d1285df662d325897f129c2beb578d0","tid":269100,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcfc271bf40ce4f7cb2c439f6ca8bcc27975bf5","tid":269100,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"529bc17496880b38f9be9df326d1db185e6a036d","tid":269100,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> blocked."},{"pid":"4f2dd13e2b3b199a1cb5ff3b5a9570e27853395a","tid":269100,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇追post <br />\n不過我覺得條友好撚悶<br />\n出到6，7個post講D阿媽係女人既野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細心睇<br />\n佢係有講中<br />\n<br />\n不過如果佢是中聯辦人士，一定會預早知答案的<br />\n<br />\n而佢其他世界大事，無5年都證實唔到"},{"pid":"96766abb9d36ab00a4cda3d1200309e4cf9bb264","tid":269100,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇追post <br />\n不過我覺得條友好撚悶<br />\n出到6，7個post講D阿媽係女人既野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/235707_3727ea389eb7c84569676a9572a31c1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F235707_3727ea389eb7c84569676a9572a31c1c.jpg&h=823afdf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/235712_85885365ace3c8389f9d3184516d16e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F235712_85885365ace3c8389f9d3184516d16e9.jpg&h=1d5c335c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/235719_2d7ff51df0437c0e6a209422d968a4ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F235719